</owl:ObjectProperty>

<owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#authorizesIn">
  Specifies the regulated zone where an authorization allows operation.
  authorizes in
  <vaem:rationale>[Ontology Generation Agent] unknown: [Ontology Generation Agent] Created object property: To indicate in which regulated zone an authorization permits operation.
    [Pitfall Resulotion Agent] Created object property: To indicate in which regulated zone an authorization permits operation.
    [Pitfall Resulotion Agent] Added inverse relationship.: To fix P19 pitfall of missing inverse relationships.</vaem:rationale>
  <dc:source>(competency_question) ¿En que zona permite operar una autorización?
    (pitfall) P19: Missing inverse relationships.</dc:source>
